Kim-ku3: Goan7 li2 hou7 chit e5 poe li7-khui goa2, chong2-si7 m7-si7 chiau3 goa2 sou2 ai3, si7 chiau3 li2 sou2 ai3. (Ma2-kho2 14:36)
U7 chit8 sou2-chai7 u7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2 mia5 kio3 Pat-long5, si7 chit8 e5 hui-siong5 phainn2, hui-siong5 ban5-phoe5, thih-khi2 e5 gin2-na2. Phah keh-piah e5 gin2-na2, kong2 peh8-chhat8, thau-theh8 mih8 lai5 chiah8......hou7 chhu3-pinn e5 lang5 chin kan-khou2 sim.
U7 chit8-pai2 iu5-goan5 cho3 phainn2, hou7 lang5 me7, chong2-si7 i chin ban5-phoe5 long2 bo5 beh jin7 m7-tioh8, bo5 beh ka7 lang5 hoe7 sit-le2. Pat-long5 in-ui7 i e5 pa-pa khi3 sio-thai5, hou7 lang5 thai5-si2, sou2-i2 chi2-u7 kap ma-ma cho3-hoe2 toa3 na7-tiann7. Sou2-i2 i e5 ma-ma eng7 chin ho2-chhui3, un5-un5-a2 ka7 i kong2 li2 m7-tioh8, sou2-i2 tioh8 ka7 lang5 kiu5 sia3-bian2, chong2-si7 i ia7 long2 tenn3 m7-chai. In ma-ma koh eng7 che7-che7 phi3-ju7, eng7 che7-che7 e5 to7-li2 ka7 i kong2 chong2-si7 long2 bo5 beh chu-tau2, na2 chhin-chhiunn7 khoann3-cho3 chau7-liam7-po5 m7 chhap i. Chong2-si7 kau3 12 tiam2, i2-keng chin ai3 khun3 lah, kou-put-chiong eng7 chhui3-boe2 kong2: ¡§Goa2 m7-tioh8, chhiann2 sia3-bian2.¡¨ Chu7 an2-ni bih loh8-khi3 khun3. Kau3 keh cha2-khi2 long2 boe7 ki3-tit liau2-liau2 lah.
Chong2-si7 tioh8 koh khai-si2 cha2-khi2 e5 le2-pai3, sui-jian5 chi2-u7 2 e5 lang5, gim5-si, thak8 Seng3-keng liau2, in ma-ma chiu7 khai-si2 ki5-to2. Ma-ma ki5-to2 kong2 Pat-long5 oe7 hiah-nih phainn2 si7 ui7-tioh8 goa2 e5 m7-tioh8, ui7-tioh8 goa2 e5 ham-ban7, ui7-tioh8 goa2 e5 ...... tit8-tit8 lau5 bak8-sai2 tui3 Siong7-te3 kiu5 sia3-bian2. Kim3 boe7-tiau5 e5 bak8-sai2, chin kan-khou2 sim teh ki5-to2 kau3 20 hun, 30 hun ...... Nge7-sim, ban5-phoe5 e5 Pat-long5 ia7 thiann chit e5 ki5-to2, tui3 sim-te2 lai5 hoan2-hoe2, jin7 m7-tioh8. Koat-sim kong2: ¡§Na7 tioh8 hou7 ma-ma chiah-nih kan-khou2, goa2 tek-khak m7 koh cho3 phainn2 lah.¡¨ Chit-khoan2 lau7-bu2 e5 bak8-sai2 chit8-pai2 koh chit8-pai2 e5 tiong-kan, Pat-long5 chin-chiann3 oann7 cho3 sin e5 lang5. Hian7-si5 teh cho3 bok8-su, ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 teh cho3 kang.
Ia5-sou lau5 hoeh-koann7 e5 ki5-to2, ia7-si7 chhoa7 lan2 kau3 tit-tioh8 kiu3--e5. Kiam2 m7-si7 chin thang kam2-sia7?
3 Geh8 15 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Lin2 na7 kiann5 Goa2 sou2 beng7-leng7 lin2 e5, chiu7-si7 Goa2 e5 peng5-iu2. (Iok-han7 15:14)
Sio2 peng5-iu2 lin2 ti7 hak8-hau7 u7 ho2 peng5-iu2 a2-bo5? U7 kui2 e5? Ti7 lin2 chhu3-pinn u7 ho2 peng5-iu2 a2-bo5? U7 kui2-e5? In khah-siong5 kap li2 choe3-hoe2 chhong3 sim2-mih8? Choe3-hoe2 thit-tho5, choe3-hoe2 iong7-kong, sim2-mih8? Choe3-hoe2 oan-ke, ji5-chhiann2 sann pang-chan7. Tai7-ke siong-ho2, sann chiau3-kou3, bo5 sio-hai7. Lin2 u7 hoann-hi2 chit-khoan2 peng5-iu2 a2-bo5? Goa2 siong-sin3 lan2 long2 ai3 u7 ho2 peng5-iu2, na2 che7-e5 na2 ho2. Siat-su2 na7 u7 lang5 long2 ai3 bo5 peng5-iu2, li2 siunn7 ho2--bo5? Un2-tang3 chin kan-khou2, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 bo5 phoann7, bo5 lang5 beh kap i thit-tho5, thak8-chheh be7-hiau2 ia7 bo5 lang5 beh sann pang-chan7. Koh siat-su2 na7 tu2-tioh8 phainn2-lang5 beh hai7--i, ia7 bo5 lang5 thang ui7--i. Li2 siunn7 u7 ho2 e5 peng5-iu2 si7 ho5-teng2 e5 iau3-kin2.
Tann lan2 cha2-khi2 ti7 chia sann-kap lai5 siunn7 lan2 e5 Chu2 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e5 kan-khou2, chin-chiann3 tat8-tit lan2 hoan2-seng2 e5 sou2-chai7. Lan2 e5 Chu2 tng i beh si2 e5 i2-cheng5 chin-chiann3 ui7-tioh8 lan2 siu7 ban7-poann e5 kan-khou2, chhin-chhiunn7 lan2 chai I u7 siu7 kong-hoe7 bo5 kong-to7 e5 sim2-mng7 kap phoann3-koat, koh hou7 peng-teng hi2-lang7, pinn7 chhi3-a2 e5 bian2-liu5 ka7 i ti3, chhi3-a2 chit8-ki, chit8-ki long2 tuh8-jip8 i e5 thau5-khak, huih chim-chim-lau5. Koh eng7 lou7-tek-a2 ka7 i ng bak8-chiu, chiah ka7 i sian3 chhui3-phoe2, koh ka7 i cheng, chiah mng7 i khoann3 chit-pai2 to2 chit8 e5 phah--i.
Koh ka7 i pak8-iap-au7 eng7 pinn ka7 i phah, phah kau3 thong seng-khu long2 ou-chhinn, che7-che7 khang long2 lau5-huih. Thong-mi5 bo5 khun3, lai5 siu7 pah-poann bo5-li2 e5 sim2-mng7 kap heng5-hoat8. Na7-si7 lan2 e5 Chu2 long2 bo5 hian2-chhut m7-kam-goan7, a2-si7 hoan2-khong3 e5 khoan2. Chong2-si7 ki5-sit8 ti7 i e5 sim-te2, iau2-u7 pi2 chiah e5 hou7 i e5 sim koh-khah kan-khou2 e5 su7. Lin2 siunn7 he si7 sim2-mih8? Chiu7-si7 iu2-cheng5 e5 poe7-poan7.
Li2 khoann3, Chu2 e7 hou7 lang5 liah8, goan5-in ti7 to2-ui7? Kiam2-m7-si7 hou7 i e5 hak8-seng Iu5-tai7 sou2 be7 mah? Chiong chi3 chhin-ai3 e5 sian-sinn be7 lang5 30 khou. An2-ni chiu7 chhoa7 phainn2-lang5 giah8 thui5, giah8 to, chhoa7 peng lai5 chhin-chhiunn7 teh liah8 kiong5-to7 e5 khoan2 lai5 liah8 Ia5-sou. Ji5-chhiann2 kau3-ui7 koh eng7 chim-chhui3, choe3 te7-it chhin-bit8, thiann3-sim e5 ki3-ho7 lai5 tui3 Chu2 chheng2-an. Eng7 an2-ni choe3 am3-ho7 lai5 kio3 lang5 liah8 sian-sinn. Li2 siunn7 chit-khoan2 hak8-seng u7 iu2-gi5 a2-bo5?
Koh li2 khoann3 Iok-han7, Iok-han7 peng5-si5 si7 Chu2 sou2 thiann3 e5 hak8-seng. Bo5-lun7 ti7 pian3-hoa3 iong5-mau7 e5 soann, ti7 Gai5-lou2 e5 tau, chiah8 boan2-chhan e5 si5 che7 ti7 Ia5-sou e5 sin-pinn, hiann3 ti7 sian-sinn e5 heng-cheng5, kap Chu2 tek8-piat8 chhin-bit8 lai5 kong2-oe7. Kau3-si5 toa7-kiann, pang3-sak i e5 goa7-sann piann3 chau2, long2 m7-kann2 koh oat8-thau5, bo5 chit8-tiam2 hian2-beng5 siau3-liam7 sian-sinn e5 khoan2-sit.
Koh li2 khoann3 Pi2-tek, Pi2-tek peng5-si5 kek8 jiat8-sim, kek8 ho2-tann2 jin7 Chu2. I bat kiann5 chui2-bin7 chiu7-kin7 Chu2. I kap Nga2-kok, Iok-han7 tak8-pai2 tek8-piat8 siu7 Chu2 e5 khan-ka3. I the3 hak8-seng hoat-piau2 i3-kian3, seng5-jin7 Ia5-sou si7 tok8-it-chin chin-oah8 Siong7-te3 e5 Kiann2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, Chu2 o-lo2 i choe3 chioh8-poann5. I ti7 Chu2 e5 bin7-cheng5 chiu3-choa7 beh kap Chu2 sann-kap si2. Tann chainn2-iunn7, keng3-jian5 chiau3 Chu2 sou2 kong2, ke boe7-thi5 e5 tai7-seng, sann-pai2 m7-jin7 Chu2. Ah! Sit8-chai7 chin kian3-siau3, koh kau3-giah8 e5 bo5 cheng5.
Koh ki5-thann e5 bin5-chiong3, che7-che7 si7 cheng5 siu7 Chu2 i-ti7, chiah8 Chu2 e5 piann2, bat thiann Chu2 kong2 to7-li2, hek8-chia2 kui2-jit8 cheng5 chiah tai7-ke chho3 chhiu7-ki, eng7 hoe, eng7 sann phou-lou7, chiap Chu2 khia5-lu5 jip8 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 siann5 e5 lang5. Kin-a2-jit8 keng3-jian5 long2 pian3-sim lai5 kong-kek Ia5-sou.
Li2 siunn7 lan2 e5 Chu2 chhin-chhiunn7 an2-ni si3-pinn long2 si7 hoan2-tui3, kong-kek. I e5 sim kan-khou2 mah? Chu7-jian5 chin kan-khou2, chong2-si7 ki5-tiong te7-it kan-khou2 e5 chiu7-si7 iu2-cheng5 e5 poe7-poan7, che-si7 hian2-beng5 bo5-cheng5, thiann3-sim e5 pheng-hoai, Mou5-kui2 sou2 choe3 choe3-toa7 khou2-ounn3 e5 su7, hui2-biat8 thiann3-sim. Chu2 kin-a2-jit8 tui3 lan2 iau3-kiu5, chhiat-chhiat ng3-bang7 lan2 tui3 I po2-siu2 chhin-bit8 e5 iu2-cheng5. Koh lan2 sann-kap choe3 sin3-tou5 e5 tiong-kan ia7 tioh8 si5-si5 po2-siu2 chit e5 thiann3 e5 iu2-cheng5. I kong2, ¡§Lin2 na7 kiann5 Goa2 sou2 beng7-leng7 lin2 e5, chiu7-si7 goa2 e5 peng5-iu2.¡¨ (Iok-han7 15:14) Sio2 peng5-iu2 tui3 chia khi2 goan7 lan2 tai7-ke sann-kap lai5 siu2 Chu2 e5 ka3-si7, sann-kap lai5 choe3 I e5 peng5-iu2.
