Kim-ku3: Pe7 ah, sia3-bian2 in, in-ui7 in sou2 choe3 e5 in m7-chai. (Lou7-ka 23:34)
A-lin5 chiu7-si7 Seng3-tek kok-bin5 hak8-hau7 e5 4 ni5 seng, ti7 hak8-hau7 thak8-chheh chin iu-siu3, ia7-si7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 bou7-hoan7-seng. I e5 pa-pa toa3 ti7 gin5-hang5, ui7-tioh8 choan2-khin5 khi3 pat8-ui7, A-lin5 ia7 choan2-hak8 kau3 Kong-hok8 kok-bin5 hak8-hau7, tu2-chiah choan2-hak8 long2 bo5 peng5-iu2, hak8-seng u7 lang5 soa3 ai3 me7 i ¡§Ia5-sou kau3¡¨. Chong2-si7 i chin gau5 thak8-chheh ho2 kui-ki2, lau7-su chin thiann3 i, hak8-seng na2 m7-goan7 tek8-piat8 thak8 1 mia5 e5 Phok-bun5 e5 seng5-chek hou7 A-lin5 jiok-koe3. Phok-bun5 chiu7 koh-khah bo5 hoann-hi2 A-lin5, soa3 sai2-long7 hak8-seng mai3 kap i kong2-oe7.
U7 chit8-jit8 A-lin5 pang3-oh8 chiu7 sui5-si5 tng2-khi3. Phok-bun5 kap kui2-na7 e5 hak8-seng siunn7 hoat-tou7 ai3 beh hai7 A-lin5, chiu7 chiong lau7-su e5 toh-teng2 kap thoa-a2 ka7 i chhiau kah loan7-chhau-chhau. Chiu7 kap kui2-na7 e5 hak8-seng khi3 pan7-kong-sek chhoe7 lau7-su kong2: ¡§Lau7-su, A-lin5 ka7 li2 chhiau toh-a2, ia7 chhiau kah loan7-chhau-chhau chiu7 tng2-khi3 lah.¡¨
Khi2-chhou lau7-su bo5 siong-sin3 kong2 A-lin5 chin koai i boe7 choe3 chit e5 su7. Chong2-si7 kai2-na7 e5 hak8-seng sann-kap kan-cheng3 kong2: ¡§Lau7-su ah, A-lin5 kong2 li2 chin thiann3 i boe7 ka7 i me7, na2 kong2 na2 chhiau li2 e5 thoa-a2 ouh¡¨, au7-lai5 lau7-su khi3 kau3-sek khoann3 chin-chiann3 loan7-chhau-chhau. Ti7 keh-jit8 cha2-khi2 lau7-su chiu7 kio3 A-lin5 khi2-lai5 ka7 i mng7 kiam2 u7 chhiau lau7-su e5 toh-a2, i chin ki5-koai3 chiu7 kong2 goa2 cha-hng pang3-oh8 chiu7 sui5-si5 tng2-khi3 goa2 bo5 choe3 chit e5 su7, na7-si7 lau7-su kong2, ¡§Li2 kong2 bo5, chainn2-iunn7 kui2-na7 e5 hak8-seng kong2 in u7 khoann3-kinn3?¡¨
Au7-lai5 Phok-bun5 kap kui2-na7 e5 hak8-seng chiu7 khi2-lai5 kan-cheng3, hit-si5 A-lin5 chiu7 sui5-si5 siunn7-tioh8 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 lau7-su sou2 kong2 Ia5-sou beh lai5 kiu3 lang5 hoan2-tng2 hou7 lang5 teng3 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3, ia7 Ia5-sou ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2 the3 hiah e5 teng3 i e5 lang5 ki5-to2 kong2, ¡§Pe7 ah, sia3-bian2 in, in-ui7 in e5 sou2 choe3 e5 in m7-chai¡¨, ia7 bat thiann-tioh8 lau7-su kong2, ¡§Su7-the5-hoan2 teh kong2 to7-li2 e5 si5, hou7 lang5 eng7 chioh8-thau5 tim3 iau2-ku2 i u7 ki5-to2 kong2: ¡§Chu2 ah, boh8-tit chiong chit e5 choe7 kui-ti7 in.¡¨
A-lin5 chiu7 chai in tui3 oan3-hin7 beh lai5 hai7 i, i chiu7 bo5 koh kong2 sim2-mih8 thau5-khak ann3-loh8-khi3. Lau7-su ia7 phah-sng3 si7 u7-iann2 chiu7 ka7 A-lin5 hoat8-khia7 chit8-tiam2-cheng ku2. U7 chit8-jit8 Phok-bun5 ti7 un7-tong7-tiann5 teh chau2 e5 si5 hou7 po-le5 chhak8-tioh8 kha teh lau5-huih, tu2-ho2 A-lin5 tui3 hia koe3 khoann3-tioh8 koann2-kin2 eng7 ka-ki7 e5 chhiu2-kin ka7 i pau kha, koh ainn7 i khi3 hou7-su7 hia ti7-liau5, hut-jian5 Phok-bun5 toa7-siann hau2, tui3 A-lin5 seh-sia7 koh chhe7 m7-tioh8 chiah ka7 i kong2 i2-cheng5 hou7 lau7-su hoat8-khia7 si7 i choe3 e5, soa3 kap i khi3 lau7-su hia. Phok-bun5 ti7 lau7-su e5 bin7-cheng5 jin7-choe7. Au7-lai5 lau7-su chiong A-lin5 e5 su7 the5-chhut ti7 kau3-oan5-hoe7, au7-lai5 chiu7 choe3 Kong-hok8 kok-bin5 hak8-hau7 e5 bou7-hoan7-seng. I2-au7 Phok-bun5 chiu7 kap A-lin5 choe3 ho2 peng5-iu2 chhoa7-chhut chhoa7-jip8, choan5-pan e5 hak8-seng ia7 kap A-lin5 choe3 chin ho2 e5 peng5-iu2 lah.
